fields.name: Easy Rumaki with Pineapple
fields.description: This dish combines the crunchiness of bacon and water chestnuts with the wonderful flavors of pineapple!

fields.name: Fruit Salsa and Cinnamon Chips
fields.description: Tasty fruit salsa and cinnamon tortilla chips. Great as an appetizer or a snack. Great for anytime!

fields.name: Southwestern Egg Rolls
fields.description: These aren't traditional egg rolls! Small flour tortillas are stuffed with an exciting blend of Southwestern-style ingredients, then deep fried until golden brown.

fields.name: Lime Chicken Soft Tacos
fields.description: Tortillas with sauteed chicken topped with lime, tomato, lettuce, cheese and salsa. Flavorful but not overwhelming: it's perfect!

fields.name: Spaghetti Carbonara
fields.description: A super rich, classic 'bacon and egg' spaghetti dish. This dish also makes an unusual brunch meal.

fields.name: Veggie Pizza
fields.description: Of course, you could just order out, but nothing beats a restaurant-made pizza. The sauce is so easy and hearty everyone will think we were in the kitchen all day cooking this up!

fields.name: Chocolate Covered Strawberries
fields.description: Eight fresh strawberries dipped in delicious milk chocolate (from Sweden) with white chocolate drizzled finely over them!

fields.name: Cinnamon Ice Cream
fields.description: This is a delicious treat. Creamy, but not too sweet. The cinnamon is not overpowering... You will love it!

fields.name: New York Cheesecake
fields.description: The king of all cheesecakes! This is the dessert you are looking for: thick and creamy!
